{"tid":169231,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"碧咸終於抵港及出席活動！","createTime":"2017-03-24T05:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T10:34:31.000Z","uid":31314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5848f937d717bfb83eaa4daf77e9c96e370ceff0","tid":169231,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:36:14.000Z","msg":"「萬人迷」碧咸（David Beckham）終於嚟咗香港啦！今次碧咸雖然未有喺社交網Instagram直擊自己飛抵香港，但不少粉絲亦在IG透露碧咸嘅行蹤。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來碧咸除了在今日下午2時45分會以友邦保險全球大使身份在中環海濱活動空間出席友邦香港財務策劃顧問MDRT(百萬圓桌會)大會之外，較早時候亦以一身Sharp醒西裝Look現身位於灣仔的友邦大廈，出席一個簡單嘅分享會，全程笑容滿面，暫未有因家鄉英國倫敦遭受恐怖襲擊一事而影響心情。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b2wigqhr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb2wigqhr&h=2d259212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w32uqz84\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw32uqz84&h=4af26294&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"651e92f00f5950f71a82c6742edb56503dd6723c","tid":169231,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:36:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81d42c2cfddcf9144cab1c67339da301524ebd59","tid":169231,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:37:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e58092dd581b6db650102b66ec43fa9c0138c8e1","tid":169231,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:40:19.000Z","msg":"屌...差啲見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd1d805d4c9f961cf5eab3424eab127ae6cdc73","tid":169231,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:41:03.000Z","msg":"好想同佢含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b23248cd48eed0d72355e6ea5353d5bea2f45ac","tid":169231,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"我地保險業真係威水 請到咸爺<img src=\"http://hkgalden.com/face/hkg/lol.gif\" data-thum